text: Jos Compaan (2 July 1958 - 30 December 2020) was a Dutch rower. She competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics, 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. Compaan was born in Purmerend, Netherlands. Compaan died on 30 December 2020 at the age of 62. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Dutch rowers Category:Sportspeople from Purmerend Category:Sportswomen
